Share this...FacebookTwitterHans von Storch‚Äôs Klimazwiebel site here presents a just released video featuring some IPCC lead authors that is designed, it appears, to promote alarmism and the myth that the science is settled and that it is now time for policymakers to act decisively.

At 2:05 mark of video, we clearly see the above graphic. Note it only goes back 100 years or so and already the last 15 years show a glaring divergence ‚Äì lack of correlation. If they had gone back 1000 years, there would be no correlation at all. There‚Äôs a clear attempt to deceive viewers here. That‚Äôs just one example.
Klimazwiebel asks readers to comment on the video. So far some early comments have been critical of the video‚Äôs haughty underlying message, some sharply critical. Here are some excerpts:
Richard Tol thinks the video appears ‚Äúpolicy prescriptive‚Äù.
Marcel Crok: ‚Äúnot an attempt to present a neutral picture of the state of the science‚Äù


